---
// 页脚（Footer）组件 - 全站共用
---

<footer class="footer-section">
  <div class="footer-container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <!-- 品牌介绍列 -->
      <div class="footer-col brand-col">
        <div class="logo-box">
          <div class="footer-logo"></div>
          <span class="logo-text">logo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="brand-desc">
          作为中国领先的数字化转型解决方案服务商，极智数科致力于通过深厚的技术积淀和行业洞察，为每一位客户创造可持续的数字价值。
        </p>
        <div class="social-icons">
          <a href="#" class="icon-item weibo"></a>
          <a href="#" class="icon-item calendar"></a>
          <a href="#" class="icon-item twitter"></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 核心业务列 -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3>核心业务</h3>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/solutions">行业解决方案</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services">技术服务</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">咨询服务</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">云服务</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">人工智能</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 关于极智列 -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3>关于极智</h3>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/about">公司简介</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">发展历程</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">荣誉资质</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">加入我们</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">投资者关系</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 常用链接列 -->
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3>常用链接</h3>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/cases">成功案例</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">新闻中心</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">研究报告</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">服务支持</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">合作伙伴</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 联系我们列 -->
      <div class="footer-col contact-col">
        <h3>联系我们</h3>
        <ul class="contact-list">
          <li class="contact-item">
            <span class="contact-icon phone-icon"></span>
            <span class="contact-text">400-888-2026</span>
          </li>
          <li class="contact-item">
            <span class="contact-icon location-icon"></span>
            <span class="contact-text">上海浦东新区...</span>
          </li>
          <li class="contact-item">
            <span class="contact-icon email-icon"></span>
            <span class="contact-text">service@ultradigit.com</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 底部版权栏 -->
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <div class="copyright">© 2026 昆仑时代版权所有.</div>
      <div class="bottom-links">
        <a href="#">隐私政策</a>
        <a href="#">服务条款</a>
        <a href="#">京ICP备20260408号-1</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  /* 页脚（Footer）模块样式 */
  .footer-section {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 60px 12% 30px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-top: 1px solid #eaecef;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
  }

  .footer-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* 网格布局 */
  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px repeat(4, 1fr) 220px;
    gap: 40px 30px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  /* 通用列样式 */
  .footer-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .footer-col h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* 品牌列 */
  .brand-col {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .logo-box {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: #3673e5;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .logo-text {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .brand-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* 社交图标 */
  .social-icons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .icon-item {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #f5f7fa;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .icon-item:hover {
    background: #e6f0ff;
  }

  /* 链接列表 */
  .footer-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .footer-links li a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .footer-links li a:hover {
    color: #3673e5;
  }

  /* 联系我们列 */
  .contact-col {
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
  }

  .contact-icon {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background-size: contain;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .phone-icon {
    background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="%23666"><path d="M6.62 10.79c1.44 2.83 3.76 5.14 6.59 6.59l2.2-2.2c.27-.27.67-.36 1.02-.24 1.12.37 2.33.57 3.57.57.55 0 1 .45 1 1V20c0 .55-.45 1-1 1-9.39 0-17-7.61-17-17 0-.55.45-1 1-1h3.5c.55 0 1 .45 1 1 0 1.25.2 2.45.57 3.57.11.35.03.74-.25 1.02l-2.2 2.2z"/></svg>');
  }

  .location-icon {
    background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="%23666"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5s1.12-2.5 2.5-2.5 2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z"/></svg>');
  }

  .email-icon {
    background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="%23666"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/></svg>');
  }

  .contact-text {
    color: #666;
  }

  /* 底部版权栏 */
  .footer-bottom {
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eaecef;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .copyright {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #999;
  }

  .bottom-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .bottom-links a {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #999;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .bottom-links a:hover {
    color: #3673e5;
  }

  /* 响应式适配 */
  @media (max-width: 1400px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr) 220px;
    }
    .brand-col {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr) 220px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-section {
      padding: 40px 5% 20px;
    }
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .footer-col {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .footer-col:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
    .footer-bottom {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
